Source: pgproto
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/Apaezmx/pgproto

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pgproto
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pgproto
Depends: postgresql-PGVERSION, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Native Protobuf support for PostgreSQL
  pgproto adds native Protobuf parsing, mutation, indexing, and JSON
  conversion support to PostgreSQL as a C extension.
